    <shortdesc class="- topic/shortdesc " xtrf="file:/Users/ilovan/CWRC%20Documentation%20-%20everything/DITA_Files-Various_Applications/CWRC-Writer/Embed_Annotate.dita" xtrc="shortdesc:1;5:16">CWRC-Writer provides users with the opportunity to annotate documents. This feature
