        <link href="Embed_Ref_Splash.dita" class="- topic/link " xtrf="file:/Users/ilovan/CWRC%20Documentation%20-%20everything/DITA_Files-Various_Applications/CWRC-Writer/Embed_Annotate.dita" xtrc="link:1;29:45" type="reference"><?ditaot gentext?><linktext class="- topic/linktext ">Working with CWRC-Writer in CWRC</linktext><?ditaot genshortdesc?><desc class="- topic/desc ">CWRC-Writer provides three options for users to work with their documents. Users can     view, annotate or edit documents.</desc></link>
        <link href="Embed_Create_Doc.dita" class="- topic/link " xtrf="file:/Users/ilovan/CWRC%20Documentation%20-%20everything/DITA_Files-Various_Applications/CWRC-Writer/Embed_Annotate.dita" xtrc="link:2;30:45" type="task"><?ditaot gentext?><linktext class="- topic/linktext ">Creating a document</linktext><?ditaot genshortdesc?><desc class="- topic/desc ">To create CWRC-Writer compatible documents you can either upload well formed XML         files or create a document from existing templates. </desc></link>
        <link href="Embedded_View_Doc.dita" class="- topic/link " xtrf="file:/Users/ilovan/CWRC%20Documentation%20-%20everything/DITA_Files-Various_Applications/CWRC-Writer/Embed_Annotate.dita" xtrc="link:3;31:46" type="task"><?ditaot gentext?><linktext class="- topic/linktext ">Viewing CWRC-Writer documents</linktext><?ditaot genshortdesc?><desc class="- topic/desc ">CWRC users can view any uploaded XML documents in CWRC-Writer. If the document is         locked by another user, you cannot edit or annotated the document until you get the other         users premission. </desc></link>  
        <link href="Embed_Ref_Save.dita" class="- topic/link " xtrf="file:/Users/ilovan/CWRC%20Documentation%20-%20everything/DITA_Files-Various_Applications/CWRC-Writer/Embed_Annotate.dita" xtrc="link:4;32:43" type="reference"><?ditaot gentext?><linktext class="- topic/linktext ">Saving CWRC-writer documents</linktext><?ditaot genshortdesc?><desc class="- topic/desc ">CWRC-Writer provides two options to save your changes and document. The first is a     general save action, but the second allows users to save and then exit the document.</desc></link>
        <link href="Embed_Save_Exit.dita" class="- topic/link " xtrf="file:/Users/ilovan/CWRC%20Documentation%20-%20everything/DITA_Files-Various_Applications/CWRC-Writer/Embed_Annotate.dita" xtrc="link:5;33:44" type="task"><?ditaot gentext?><linktext class="- topic/linktext ">Saving your document</linktext><?ditaot genshortdesc?><desc class="- topic/desc ">In CWRC-Writer your documents can be edited by multiple people. The “Save and Exit”         icon does as the title suggests and opens up the document for others to edit.</desc></link>
